data.description: Situated on a beautiful lot near I-85, this extraordinary Lake Hartwell custom home offers the perfect blend of luxury, privacy, and modern design. Entering the home, one feels an ambiance of affluence, all while incorporating luxurious elements of design and quality craftsmanship. The focal point of the living area is a custom rock fireplace, radiating warmth and providing the perfect ambiance for cozy evenings. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece with high-end appliances and an open floor plan for entertainment. Every detail has been meticulously thought out, from the custom cabinetry to the top-of-the-line appliances. The main floor offers two entertainment areas, two guest bedrooms, a full bath, and a porch that gifts scenery and seclusion. One of the home's primary bedroom suites is located on the top floor, vaulted ceiling, ship lap siding, heart pine floors, custom large walk-in closet, along with exquisite luxury bathroom styled with ship lap siding, huge walk in rain head shower, and two sink vanities.  In addition to the master there is a guest bedroom with closet, can be used as a guitar room or office.  The stunning bottom floor is a retreat with a private entrance and patio overlooking the lake, a chef's kitchen and entertainment area, a second master suite with a large walk-in closet, a custom-designed bathroom with a soaking tub and separate shower, multiple guest bedrooms, and a custom bunkbed room attached off the master suite. A beautiful steam marble shower adjacent to a workout room with mirrors and commercial flooring on the terrace level makes for incredible workouts. The outdoor verandah with a masonry fireplace flanks a screen porch and a gradual paved walkway to the lake. See additional documents for a complete list of custom finishes throughout the home. Take advantage of the boat dock and spend your days on the boat or simply basking in the sun. This cutting-edge Lake Hartwell estate offers a rare opportunity to own a truly remarkable property. With its modern design, stunning features, and unparalleled surroundings, this home is a haven for those seeking the perfect blend of luxury, privacy, and natural beauty. See additional documents for a complete list of custom finishes throughout the home.
